 kako bi oni mogli doživiti zajedničko sjedinjenje

569
00:38:12,660 --> 00:38:14,660
 i kasnije taj vrhunac

570
00:38:14,660 --> 00:38:18,660
 u kojem se ništa više ne mora reći.

571
00:38:19,660 --> 00:38:21,620
 Ovi koji su u braku to znaju.

572
00:38:21,620 --> 00:38:23,620
 Tad niko ništa ne govori.

573
00:38:23,620 --> 00:38:25,340
 To je trenutak u kojem često je ateisti,

574
00:38:25,340 --> 00:38:26,260
 kažu oh my god.

575
00:38:26,260 --> 00:38:30,880
 Ali Papa Ivan Pavo II

576
00:38:30,880 --> 00:38:33,520
 kaže da postoji dva predokusa

577
00:38:33,520 --> 00:38:35,960
 neba na zemlji

578
00:38:35,960 --> 00:38:37,780
 gdje možemo barem predokusom

579
00:38:37,780 --> 00:38:38,640
 osjetiti nebo.

580
00:38:38,640 --> 00:38:40,080
 Jedno je molitve na ekstaza,

581
00:38:40,080 --> 00:38:42,140
 drugi je orgazam u spolnom činu.

582
00:38:43,480 --> 00:38:44,440
 I na neki način

583
00:38:44,440 --> 00:38:46,140
 ovo slavljenje uvodi

584
00:38:46,140 --> 00:38:47,780
 u tu pomazanu tišinu

585
00:38:47,780 --> 00:38:49,040
 koja je bezvremenska.

586
00:38:49,040 --> 00:38:50,900
 I di Bog progovara.

587
00:38:50,900 --> 00:38:53,080
 Razmišljajte o tome na taj način.

588
00:38:53,080 --> 00:38:55,980
 Pa možda mladi neće tražiti

589
00:38:55,980 --> 00:38:57,220
 suroga te tudi traže

590
00:38:57,220 --> 00:38:58,040
 u bludnosti,

591
00:38:58,040 --> 00:38:59,060
 u drogi

592
00:38:59,060 --> 00:39:00,460
 i u sličnim stvarima.

593
00:39:00,460 --> 00:39:04,800
 Često se nakon slavljenja

594
00:39:04,800 --> 00:39:06,400
 događa oslobođenje.

595
00:39:06,400 --> 00:39:09,560
 Ja sam sam svjedočio

596
00:39:09,560 --> 00:39:10,560
 kako je slavljenje

597
00:39:10,560 --> 00:39:11,680
 dovelo do često

598
00:39:11,680 --> 00:39:13,180
 dramatičnih oslobađanja.

599
00:39:13,480 --> 00:39:15,500
 Sjetimo se samo dijela apostolskih

600
00:39:15,500 --> 00:39:16,960
 kad Pavao i Sila

601
00:39:16,960 --> 00:39:18,820
 svezani u okovima

602
00:39:18,820 --> 00:39:20,040
 slave Boga

603
00:39:20,040 --> 00:39:21,600
 i odjednom se od tog

604
00:39:21,600 --> 00:39:23,160
 slavljena takva sila spustila

605
00:39:23,160 --> 00:39:24,320
 su njima pali okovi

606
00:39:24,320 --> 00:39:26,160
 i vrata tamnice su se otvorila.

607
00:39:26,160 --> 00:39:29,240
 Slavljenje to čini i dan danas.

608
00:39:29,240 --> 00:39:31,460
 Otvara vrata,

609
00:39:31,460 --> 00:39:32,660
 lomi okove,

610
00:39:32,660 --> 00:39:34,240
 pušta ljude na slobodu.

611
00:39:34,240 --> 00:39:36,120
 Jedan poznati karizmatik

612
00:39:36,120 --> 00:39:37,500
 je vodio slavljeničku kuću

613
00:39:37,500 --> 00:39:38,140
 u Londonu

614
00:39:38,140 --> 00:39:39,740
 i poslali su mu

615
00:39:39,740 --> 00:39:40,980
 jednog ruskog pravoslavca

616
00:39:40,980 --> 00:39:41,960
 koji je bio opsjednut

617
00:39:41,960 --> 00:39:44,140
 jer su imali službu oslobađanja.

618
00:39:44,140 --> 00:39:46,480
 I on kad je ušao

619
00:39:46,480 --> 00:39:47,400
 i kad je vidio to

620
00:39:47,400 --> 00:39:48,480
 aleluja, slavljenje,

621
00:39:48,480 --> 00:39:49,080
 možete misliti

622
00:39:49,080 --> 00:39:50,140
 pravoslavnu liturgiju,

623
00:39:50,140 --> 00:39:51,120
 ovo što je on tamo vidio,

624
00:39:51,120 --> 00:39:52,440
 on je želio izaći.

625
00:39:52,440 --> 00:39:53,560
 A čovjek ko je vodio

626
00:39:53,560 --> 00:39:54,680
 je slavljenje mu rekao

627
00:39:54,680 --> 00:39:55,960
 ako ti izađiš,

628
00:39:55,960 --> 00:39:57,620
 on će ostati.

629
00:39:57,620 --> 00:39:59,200
 A ako ti ostaneš,

630
00:39:59,200 --> 00:39:59,960
 on će izaći.

631
00:39:59,960 --> 00:40:01,300
 Mislići na demona

632
00:40:01,300 --> 00:40:02,140
 koje ga je tlačio.

633
00:40:02,140 --> 00:40:04,940
 I čovjek je doživio oslobađanje.

634
00:40:04,940 --> 00:40:07,900
 I tu ulazim u taj četvrti korak,

635
00:40:07,900 --> 00:40:09,560
 a to je često moramo shvatiti

636
00:40:09,560 --> 00:40:10,820
 slavljenje i kao borbu.

637
00:40:10,820 --> 00:40:12,580
 Mi nismo samo hodočasnička,

638
00:40:12,580 --> 00:40:14,200
 mi smo i vojujuća crkva.

639
00:40:14,200 --> 00:40:17,240
 I slavljenje je često

640
00:40:17,240 --> 00:40:18,580
 duhovni boj

641
00:40:18,580 --> 00:40:20,560
 u kojem mi osvajamo

642
00:40:20,560 --> 00:40:21,560
 nebeski prostor.

643
00:40:21,560 --> 00:40:23,000
 Sveti Pavao rekao

644
00:40:23,000 --> 00:40:24,080
 da nam se nije borit

645
00:40:24,080 --> 00:40:25,340
 protiv tijela i krvi,

646
00:40:25,340 --> 00:40:29,040
 nego protiv vrhovništva

647
00:40:29,040 --> 00:40:29,820
 po nebesima.

648
00:40:29,820 --> 00:40:31,300
 I zato često

649
00:40:31,300 --> 00:40:32,920
 kad počinje slavljenje

650
00:40:32,920 --> 00:40:33,740
 svi izjevaju.

651
00:40:33,740 --> 00:40:35,820
 I zato često

652
00:40:35,820 --> 00:40:37,140
 zuje okolo.

653
00:40:37,140 --> 00:40:38,800
 Nije se probilo još.

654
00:40:38,800 --> 00:40:40,280
 Nema kontakta.

655
00:40:40,280 --> 00:40:43,120
 Kaže Gabriel Amort

656
00:40:43,120 --> 00:40:45,340
 da je Božja Milošta

657
00:40:45,340 --> 00:40:46,120
 ne možemo vidjeti

658
00:40:46,120 --> 00:40:47,640
 kako je izgledao nebeski prostor

659
00:40:47,640 --> 00:40:48,320
 iznad nas.

660
00:40:49,420 --> 00:40:50,100
 Vrhovništvo.

661
00:40:50,100 --> 00:40:52,080
 Ali

662
00:40:52,080 --> 00:40:54,400
 Sirah nam kaže

663
00:40:54,400 --> 00:40:55,780
 da molitva poniznog

664
00:40:55,780 --> 00:40:57,240
 prodire kroz oblake.

665
00:40:57,240 --> 00:41:00,200
 I kad se to slavljenje zažari,

666
00:41:00,200 --> 00:41:01,200
 kad je u to slavljenje

667
00:41:01,200 --> 00:41:02,140
 uključeno srce,

668
00:41:02,140 --> 00:41:02,780
 kao što kaže

669
00:41:02,780 --> 00:41:03,760
 sveta Hildegarda,

670
00:41:03,760 --> 00:41:04,840
 onda se događa

671
00:41:04,840 --> 00:41:05,560
 taj most.

672
00:41:05,560 --> 00:41:07,720
 I zato moramo moliti

673
00:41:07,720 --> 00:41:09,060
 za naše voditelje slavljenja

674
00:41:09,060 --> 00:41:09,740
 da su oni ti

675
00:41:09,740 --> 00:41:11,180
 koji u prostoru

676
00:41:11,180 --> 00:41:13,060
 gdje se vrši evangelizacija

677
00:41:13,060 --> 00:41:14,340
 stanu pred Boga

678
00:41:14,340 --> 00:41:15,740
 i probijaju

679
00:41:15,740 --> 00:41:16,940
 i vode narod

680
00:41:16,940 --> 00:41:18,280
 da se stvori

681
00:41:18,280 --> 00:41:19,020
 taj most

682
00:41:19,020 --> 00:41:20,900
 između neba,

683
00:41:20,900 --> 00:41:22,340
 između Božjeg prijestolja

684
00:41:22,340 --> 00:41:23,160
 i zemlje.

685
00:41:23,160 --> 00:41:25,060
 To je proboj

686
00:41:25,060 --> 00:41:26,040
 koji nastaje

687
00:41:26,040 --> 00:41:26,760
 slavljenjem.

688
00:41:27,680 --> 00:41:29,160
 pročitaću vam jedno svjedočanstvo

689
00:41:29,160 --> 00:41:30,080
 Johanesa Hartla,

690
00:41:30,080 --> 00:41:32,340
 čovjeka koji je proučio molitvu,

691
00:41:32,340 --> 00:41:33,780
 osnovuje domove molitve,

692
00:41:33,780 --> 00:41:35,340
 tu ima nekih koji su

693
00:41:35,340 --> 00:41:36,960
 proučavali Hartla,

694
00:41:36,960 --> 00:41:37,840
 vjerujem da ima,

695
00:41:37,840 --> 00:41:38,800
 među vama.

696
00:41:38,800 --> 00:41:39,800
 I on opisuje

697
00:41:39,800 --> 00:41:41,580
 kada su ušli u jedan park,

698
00:41:41,580 --> 00:41:44,100
 nešto slično kao što je nekad bio

699
00:41:44,100 --> 00:41:44,880
 naš ribnjak,

700
00:41:44,880 --> 00:41:46,380
 gdje su se okupljali

701
00:41:46,380 --> 00:41:48,180
 alternativci,

702
00:41:48,180 --> 00:41:49,580
 prostitutke

703
00:41:49,580 --> 00:41:51,460
 i rubne društvene skupine.

704
00:41:51,460 --> 00:41:52,680
 I pogledajte

705
00:41:52,680 --> 00:41:54,060
 koja je snaga slavljenja.

706
00:41:54,060 --> 00:41:55,260
 Oni su došli u središte

707
00:41:55,260 --> 00:41:56,020
 tog parka.

708
00:41:56,020 --> 00:41:57,120
 I kaže,

709
00:41:58,180 --> 00:41:59,320
 Zauzimamo mjesto

710
00:41:59,320 --> 00:42:00,380
 u sredini parka

711
00:42:00,380 --> 00:42:01,560
 i počinjemo pjevati.

712
00:42:01,560 --> 00:42:03,560
 Ja sviram gitaru.

713
00:42:03,560 --> 00:42:05,460
 Podrugljiv smijeh

714
00:42:05,460 --> 00:42:06,760
 već kod prvih akorda.

715
00:42:06,760 --> 00:42:08,360
 Na leđima mogu osjetiti

716
00:42:08,360 --> 00:42:09,900
 poglede veselih punkera.

717
00:42:09,900 --> 00:42:11,920
 Moraju biti na stotine

718
00:42:11,920 --> 00:42:13,620
 koje se ovdje svaki dan sastaju

719
00:42:13,620 --> 00:42:15,040
 u potradi za drogom,

720
00:42:15,040 --> 00:42:16,600
 seksom i malo novaca.

721
00:42:16,600 --> 00:42:18,300
 Mi stojimo u krugu.

722
00:42:18,300 --> 00:42:20,120
 Usred pločnika

723
00:42:20,120 --> 00:42:22,060
 i između krhotina stakla.

724
00:42:22,060 --> 00:42:24,060
 Za čitave prve pjesme

725
00:42:24,060 --> 00:42:24,980
 uopće ne molim.

726
00:42:24,980 --> 00:42:26,440
 Zatvaram oči

727
00:42:26,440 --> 00:42:27,440
 i zaokupljen sam

728
00:42:27,440 --> 00:42:28,700
 samo time da ne mislim

729
00:42:28,700 --> 00:42:29,480
 na poglede

730
00:42:29,480 --> 00:42:30,920
 koji su u mene uperani.

731
00:42:30,920 --> 00:42:33,080
 Ozreće je tjeskobno,

732
00:42:33,080 --> 00:42:33,880
 tama.

733
00:42:33,880 --> 00:42:35,500
 Hoću otići,

734
00:42:35,500 --> 00:42:36,740
 ali sviram dalje.

735
00:42:36,740 --> 00:42:39,560
 Kod druge pjesme

736
00:42:39,560 --> 00:42:41,160
 postoje nešto jednostavnije.

737
00:42:41,160 --> 00:42:42,520
 Ti si uzvišen,

738
00:42:42,520 --> 00:42:43,680
 gospodine, pjevamo.

739
00:42:43,680 --> 00:42:46,000
 I malčice počinjem vjerovati.

740
00:42:46,000 --> 00:42:47,560
 Kod treće pjesme

741
00:42:47,560 --> 00:42:48,480
 stanje ovakvo.

742
00:42:48,480 --> 00:42:50,960
 Okolina je u velike isključena

743
00:42:50,960 --> 00:42:52,600
 i naša je pozornost

744
00:42:52,600 --> 00:42:53,520
 više usmjerena

745
00:42:53,520 --> 00:42:54,700
 na Božju veličinu

746
00:42:54,700 --> 00:42:56,820
 nego na bjedne okolnosti

747
00:42:56,820 --> 00:42:57,960
 u kojima se nalazimo.

748
00:42:57,960 --> 00:43:00,180
 Podrugljiv smijeh je prestao.

749
00:43:00,180 --> 00:43:02,360
 Postoje nam lakše u srcu

750
00:43:02,360 --> 00:43:03,560
 i slavljenje teče.

751
00:43:03,560 --> 00:43:05,600
 Pjevamo o Isusovu svijetlu

752
00:43:05,600 --> 00:43:06,720
 koje razbija tamu,

753
00:43:06,720 --> 00:43:08,020
 ali odjednom

754
00:43:08,020 --> 00:43:09,080
 kao da se nešto

755
00:43:09,080 --> 00:43:10,480
 miješalo u naše pjevanje.

756
00:43:11,160 --> 00:43:12,240
 Tko to krivo pjeva

757
00:43:12,240 --> 00:43:12,880
 pjeva pored mene?

758
00:43:12,880 --> 00:43:14,380
 Ovo mi zvuči na Vigora.

759
00:43:14,380 --> 00:43:17,080
 Otvaram oči.

760
00:43:17,080 --> 00:43:18,540
 To su dvojica

761
00:43:18,540 --> 00:43:19,320
 bezkućnika

762
00:43:19,320 --> 00:43:20,360
 s bocom u ruci

763
00:43:20,360 --> 00:43:22,240
 koji su nam se pridružili

764
00:43:22,240 --> 00:43:24,240
 i očito hoće pjevati s nama.

765
00:43:24,240 --> 00:43:26,160
 Iz kosa nam se približava

766
00:43:26,160 --> 00:43:27,100
 jedan drugi lik.

767
00:43:27,100 --> 00:43:27,960
 To je dama

768
00:43:27,960 --> 00:43:29,200
 ispjena izgleda,

769
00:43:29,200 --> 00:43:30,800
 crveno obojene kose

770
00:43:30,800 --> 00:43:31,960
 i pokvorenih zubi.

771
00:43:31,960 --> 00:43:34,160
 I ona pokušava pjevati s nama.

772
00:43:34,980 --> 00:43:36,280
 Ponovo zatvaram oči.

773
00:43:36,280 --> 00:43:37,540
 Sada su sloboda

774
00:43:37,540 --> 00:43:38,940
 i radost zamjetljivi.

775
00:43:38,940 --> 00:43:41,040
 Okolina je zaboravljena,

776
00:43:41,040 --> 00:43:43,100
 a ja sam posve u slavljenju.

777
00:43:43,100 --> 00:43:44,920
 Kada sam sljedeći put

778
00:43:44,920 --> 00:43:45,720
 otvorio oči,

779
00:43:45,720 --> 00:43:47,180
 to sam učinio zbog toga

780
00:43:47,180 --> 00:43:48,860
 što samo ja još pjevam.

781
00:43:48,860 --> 00:43:50,580
 Što je s drugima?

782
00:43:50,580 --> 00:43:51,940
 Iznenađen vidim

783
00:43:51,940 --> 00:43:52,860
 da su udubljeni

784
00:43:52,860 --> 00:43:53,960
 u razgovor s ljudima

785
00:43:53,960 --> 00:43:55,600
 koji su se iz svih pravaca

786
00:43:55,600 --> 00:43:57,200
 uputili prema našem krugu

787
00:43:57,200 --> 00:43:58,840
 i hoće su djelovati

788
00:43:58,840 --> 00:44:00,500
 u onome što se ovdje zbiva.

789
00:44:00,500 --> 00:44:02,220
 Nije potrebalo dugo

790
00:44:02,220 --> 00:44:04,060
 i svi mi zajedno pjevamo,

791
00:44:04,620 --> 00:44:06,780
 a potekle su i prve suze.

792
00:44:06,780 --> 00:44:09,660
 Napokon odlažem svoju gitaru

793
00:44:09,660 --> 00:44:11,400
 jer nakon što jedan drogeras čuo

794
00:44:11,400 --> 00:44:13,160
 da smo molili za njegova prijatelja

795
00:44:13,160 --> 00:44:14,100
 i on bi to htio.

796
00:44:14,100 --> 00:44:16,200
 Prostitutki, alkoholičari

797
00:44:16,200 --> 00:44:16,960
 mole s nama,

798
00:44:16,960 --> 00:44:18,720
 otvaraju srce Isusu

799
00:44:18,720 --> 00:44:20,340
 kao svom spasitelju

800
00:44:20,340 --> 00:44:21,500
 i izbavitelju.

801
00:44:21,500 --> 00:44:23,460
 Jedan čovjek govori sa mnom.

802
00:44:23,460 --> 00:44:25,140
 Čitavo njegovo tijelo,

803
00:44:25,140 --> 00:44:25,980
 čitavo lice,

804
00:44:25,980 --> 00:44:27,240
 čak i koža na glavi

805
00:44:27,240 --> 00:44:28,800
 i trepavice su tetovirani.

806
00:44:28,800 --> 00:44:30,480
 Izgleda kao reptil

807
00:44:30,480 --> 00:44:32,020
 i onda pripovjeda otcu

808
00:44:32,020 --> 00:44:33,040
 koji ga je zlostavljao

809
00:44:33,040 --> 00:44:34,060
 kako je postao

810
00:44:34,260 --> 00:44:35,000
 homoseksualac

811
00:44:35,000 --> 00:44:35,840
 kako se počeo

812
00:44:35,840 --> 00:44:37,120
 prostituirati na ulici.

813
00:44:37,120 --> 00:44:38,860
 I posvuda možemo čuti

814
00:44:38,860 --> 00:44:40,540
 kako se pripovjeda o Isusu,

815
00:44:40,540 --> 00:44:42,120
 moli i doživljava

816
00:44:42,120 --> 00:44:43,440
 kako se Božja ljubav

817
00:44:43,440 --> 00:44:44,420
 uljeva u srca.

818
00:44:44,420 --> 00:44:46,040
 Nemamo kod sebe

819
00:44:46,040 --> 00:44:47,140
 prikladnih knjižica

820
00:44:47,140 --> 00:44:48,500
 jer nismo računali

821
00:44:48,500 --> 00:44:49,520
 sa ovakvim ishodom.

822
00:44:49,520 --> 00:44:50,400
 Kaže,

823
00:44:50,980 --> 00:44:52,100
 pa neki od nas daraju

824
00:44:52,100 --> 00:44:53,400
 svoje vlastite Biblije.

825
00:44:53,400 --> 00:44:54,940
 Suze, smijeh,

826
00:44:54,940 --> 00:44:55,700
 molitva

827
00:44:55,700 --> 00:44:56,560
 i pjevanje

828
00:44:56,560 --> 00:44:57,360
 na posljedku

829
00:44:57,360 --> 00:44:59,040
 ispunja u čitav prostor.

830
00:44:59,040 --> 00:45:01,100
 I kada nekoliko sati

831
00:45:01,100 --> 00:45:02,060
 kasnije odlazimo,

832
00:45:02,060 --> 00:45:02,820
 domahuje nam

833
00:45:02,820 --> 00:45:03,780
 kao prijateljima

834
